---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { getLiveRates } from '../utils/rates';
const ratesData = await getLiveRates(Astro);
---

<BaseLayout
  keywords="about MortgageDash, free mortgage calculator team, our mission, mortgage calculator, home loan calculator, current mortgage rates, monthly mortgage payment, free mortgage calculator, mortgage payment calculator, house payment calculator, home mortgage calculator, calculate mortgage, mortgage estimator, monthly house payment, mortgage interest calculator, loan payment calculator, how much is my mortgage, mortgage calculator with taxes, mortgage calculator with PMI, mortgage calculator with insurance, PITI calculator, home buying calculator, home affordability calculator, mortgage amortization, what will my mortgage payment be, mortgage calculator 2025, best mortgage calculator, accurate mortgage calculator, simple mortgage calculator, mortgage calculator USA, home loan payment estimator, mortgage rate calculator, mortgage cost calculator"
  canonicalUrl="/about/"
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn more about MortgageDash and our mission to provide accurate, easy-to-use mortgage tools."
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 pb-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
        About
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#06b6d4] to-[#10b981] bg-clip-text text-transparent">MortgageDash</span>
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-8 sm:p-12 space-y-6">
      <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
        Buying a home is one of the most significant financial decisions you'll ever make. Yet, for too long, web-based mortgage calculators have relied on intrusive pop-ups, disruptive layouts, or hidden paywalls that degrade the user experience.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
        <strong>MortgageDash was built to fix that.</strong>
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
        We provide clean, fast, and completely free financial tools. Our calculators are pre-loaded with highly accurate state-by-state data—including precise property tax averages and insurance estimates—so you get the real numbers, no guesswork required.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
        Whether you are buying your first home, trying to pay off your loan early, or wondering if you should refinance, MortgageDash gives you the clarity you need to make confident decisions.
      </p>
      <div class="pt-6 border-t mt-8" style="border-color: var(--border-default);">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">Editorial Review & Authorship</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
          All tools, calculators, and educational content on MortgageDash are authored and strictly reviewed by <strong>Karteek Tadimalla, Founder</strong>. We adhere to rigorous editorial standards to ensure all calculations and state-specific insights reflect real, verifiable data to protect homebuyers from misinformation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div id="methodology" class="pt-6 border-t mt-8" style="border-color: var(--border-default);">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">Methodology: How We Calculate Your Numbers</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          Our calculators use the standard fully-amortizing <strong>PITI formula</strong> (Principal, Interest, Taxes, and Insurance) to ensure you see the true cost of homeownership, not just a deceptively low principal and interest baseline.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#10b981] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            <span><strong>Principal & Interest:</strong> Calculated using standard amortization formulas (<code>M = P [ i(1 + i)^n ] / [ (1 + i)^n - 1 ]</code>).</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#06b6d4] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            <span><strong>Interest Rates:</strong> Our default interest rates are automatically pulled from the official <strong>Federal Reserve Economic Data (FRED) API</strong> to ensure you are running simulations on current market realities.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#f59e0b] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            <span><strong>Taxes & Insurance:</strong> Our localized calculators use a custom <code>states.json</code> database built from aggregated, state-specific effective property tax rates and average homeowners insurance premiums.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-6 border-t mt-8" style="border-color: var(--border-default);">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--text-primary);">Our Core Principles</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#10b981] shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            <span><strong>Privacy First Calculator:</strong> Your financial inputs (income, down payment) are processed entirely locally and never stored on our servers.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#06b6d4] shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            <span><strong>Design First:</strong> Beautiful, intuitive interfaces that are easy to use on any device.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#f59e0b] shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
            <span><strong>Accuracy:</strong> Incorporating real-world tax and insurance data for all 50 states.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
